00:01:23.900 --> 00:01:25.260
Serve my father his tea.

00:01:27.820 --> 00:01:28.620
Hurry up.

00:01:43.580 --> 00:01:44.980
I know you want revenge,

00:01:45.980 --> 00:01:47.580
