00:10:04.460 --> 00:10:05.860
Are you really going to the wedding?

00:10:08.060 --> 00:10:09.140
I'm going to the wedding.

00:10:09.180 --> 00:10:10.420
Let me go! I'm going to the wedding!

00:10:12.180 --> 00:10:13.100
Have you forgotten everything?

00:10:25.220 --> 00:10:27.460
This is the Tiger-Head Lock
I gave you at the orphanage.

00:10:28.060 --> 00:10:29.220
And the candy I stole for you
back then...

00:10:29.580 --> 00:10:31.540
Can't you find it in yourself
to trust me, just this once?

00:10:37.700 --> 00:10:38.500
I'm sorry.

00:10:39.780 --> 00:10:40.980
I was wrong.

00:10:42.500 --> 00:10:44.260
I shouldn't have
left the orphanage alone.

00:10:45.020 --> 00:10:46.580
I broke our promise first.

00:10:47.180 --> 00:10:48.780
But you've already died once.

00:10:49.380 --> 00:10:50.300
I can't...

00:10:50.580 --> 00:10:51.260
I can't stand by

00:10:51.260 --> 00:10:52.780
